Schuyler Grant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schuyler_Grant 0 Schuyler Grant (born Schuyler DeBarthe Ranson Grant; April 29, 1970) is a former American actress best known for supporting roles in television, including the popular Anne of Green Gables mini-series.
